    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next adventure with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior looks great, making it the perfect companion for daily commutes or weekend getaways!",
