    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, reflecting a history of consistent maintenance. While the exterior looks great overall, you will find some minor blemishes such as light surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the hood consistent with its age. The interior is clean and smoke-free, with all major electronic features and climate control systems fully functional. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
