    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine struggles to maintain a consistent idle and there are noticeable mechanical issues with the transmission that will require a professional overhaul. The exterior shows significant wear, including several dents and areas of rust, while the interior requires a deep cleaning and repair of the upholstery. It is not currently in reliable driving condition and will likely need to be towed.",
