    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standards, it offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior cabin, reflects an uncompromising commitment to quality. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless vehicle.",
      "price": 43500.0,
